    {
      "id": "2035535819180741065",
      "text": "RT @FutureJurvetson: T͢E͢R͢A͢F͢A͢B͢ Launch  ⌨  \nGoal: adding a trillion watts of compute, 2x the entire U.S. electricity market, every year…",
      "created_at": "Sun Mar 22 01:55:32 +0000 2026",
      "lang": "en",
      "media": [],
      "retweet": {
        "id": "2035529409797775658",
        "text": "T͢E͢R͢A͢F͢A͢B͢ Launch  ⌨  \nGoal: adding a trillion watts of compute, 2x the entire U.S. electricity market, every year.  A new 2nm fab to build ~1 billion AI chips/year. Most will be in space.\n\n\"We have an announcement to make: the most epic chip-building effort by far.\" — @ElonMusk tonight\n\nLive now  ► https://t.co/7TBBDAE8Nf",
        "created_at": "Sun Mar 22 01:30:04 +0000 2026",
